                <p><strong>Who connects the room:</strong> The in-person videographer</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>If in-person vid has NOT connected 10 minutes before start:</strong> Alert #video-help immediately</li>
                    <li>Depo Support will reach out to the in-person vid provider for updates</li>
                    <li><strong>If you claimed Host:</strong> Pass Host privileges to the In-Person Videographer before exiting</li>
