                <p><strong>Who connects the room:</strong> The in-person Court Reporter</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>If in-person CR has NOT connected 10 minutes before start:</strong> Call the in-person CR directly using the phone number in your Provider Dashboard</li>
                    <li>If you cannot get a direct update from the CR, post to #video-help</li>
                    <li><strong>If you claimed Host:</strong> Pass Host privileges to the Court Reporter before exiting</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="reset-btn" onclick="resetHybridTree()">Start Over</button>
            </div>
            
